        "response": {
          "bodySize": 999,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 999,
            "text": "{\"id\":\"msg_01MSmDrEuXV687z6C4knA5va\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"model\":\"claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Modern E-Commerce Platform\\n\\nYour request brings to mind sleek marketplaces like Shopify and Square, with clean interfaces and smooth user flows that build trust and encourage exploration.\\n\\n**Design Inspiration:**\\n- Minimalist product cards with hover effects\\n- Soft, professional color palette\\n- Animated micro-interactions\\n\\n**Key Features:**\\n- Secure user authentication system\\n- Product catalog with search and filters \\n- Shopping cart with persistent storage\\n- User profiles and order history\\n- Responsive checkout process\\n\\nWait a moment while I build your landing page.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":305,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":124,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
