            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1991,
            "text": "{\n  \"id\": \"chatcmpl-CYd7XmYEwMWM9FxXWbOpG0PE6PbDn\",\n  \"object\": \"chat.completion\",\n  \"created\": 1762369567,\n  \"model\": \"gpt-5-2025-08-07\",\n  \"choices\": [\n    {\n      \"index\": 0,\n      \"message\": {\n        \"role\": \"assistant\",\n        \"content\": \"**Vision:** A cinematic, awe-filled landing page that invites visitors to journey from Earth to the edges of the observable universe, blending science, history, and the near future.  \\n**Design inspiration:** NASA’s archival imagery and data aesthetics, SpaceX minimalism, Apple-style narrative sections, and Interstellar-grade typography on a dark starfield canvas with subtle parallax nebulae and tasteful glassmorphism.  \\n**Visual system:** Palette of deep-space navy-to-black with ion-thruster blues and solar-gold accents; typography pairing a bold geometric grotesk for headlines with a humanist sans for body; motion via micro-animations, scroll-driven reveals, and gentle constellation particles for depth and wonder.  \\n**First-version features:** Hero section with mission tagline and primary CTA; mission timeline (Apollo → Artemis/Starship) with rich imagery; interactive solar system/mission map; live “Latest Discoveries” feed from NASA/ESA APIs; astronaut and spacecraft spotlights; educational explainers (How Rockets Work, Life in Microgravity); newsletter signup and donation/volunteer CTAs; performance, accessibility, and SEO foundations.  \\nWait a moment while I build your landing page.\",\n        \"refusal\": null,\n        \"annotations\": []\n      },\n      \"finish_reason\": \"stop\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"usage\": {\n    \"prompt_tokens\": 272,\n    \"completion_tokens\": 1464,\n    \"total_tokens\": 1736,\n    \"prompt_tokens_details\": {\n      \"cached_tokens\": 0,\n      \"audio_tokens\": 0\n    },\n    \"completion_tokens_details\": {\n      \"reasoning_tokens\": 1216,\n      \"audio_tokens\": 0,\n      \"accepted_prediction_tokens\": 0,\n      \"reject